{"tid":411126,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"消防員工餘看A片：這體型好眼熟　驚覺同袍兼差拍60部AV","createTime":"2017-09-23T14:09:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-23T14:47:21.000Z","uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c9bedaa9d999a03df64a872d749ddf4731911bad","tid":411126,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T14:09:45.000Z","msg":"日本色情產業發達，每年除了有許多新的AV女優出道，也有不少男性抱著「一展長才」的美夢入行，但一不小心就可能被同事認出。日本櫪木縣一名26歲的消防員在工作之餘，還悄悄兼差拍了60部A片，時間長達近1年半！<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2813/d2813476.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2813%2Fd2813476.jpg&h=3528f5e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲日本色情產業發達。示意圖，非本文當事人<br />\n<br />\n據日媒報導，該消防員的同事2016年8月在網路上欣賞A片時，意外發現男優的體型和他很相似，但當時有馬賽克遮臉的關係，事情也在他否認後不了了之。沒想到，到了今年4月時，又有同事發現了沒打馬賽克的版本，兼差拍AV的事情就此曝光。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2813/d2813479.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2813%2Fd2813479.jpg&h=ec08e74e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲消防員兼差拍AV被同事發現。<br />\n<br />\n事後，該消防員向上級坦言，是在健身房運動時被友人介紹去拍A片的，為了盡快還清貸款，沒想太多就答應了，從2016年4月一直拍到今年8月，總共約60部作品，共入帳90萬日幣（約24萬新台幣）。基沙文對於這宗交易非常歡迎，希望哥斯達回歸有助球隊增加戰鬥力。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2813/d2813478.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2813%2Fd2813478.jpg&h=20a2e7d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲消防高層出面鞠躬道歉。<br />\n<br />\n該消防總部21日特別開記者會說明來龍去脈，並表示原本該消防員要被處以停職半年的處分，但當事人已提出辭呈並獲准，總部進一步指出，所有人員要事前經過許可才能兼差，但因當事人沒有先告知，所以構成了欺瞞行為，才決定予以處分。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/fcZkpL_eruQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FfcZkpL_eruQ&d=CU0xZXF8PN25iZTvszaXNJUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=8b0dde0f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/fcZkpL_eruQ</a>"},{"pid":"1d3d8cd99e2d8aedb4fde084209bee98a0623508","tid":411126,"uid":38516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T14:11:05.000Z","msg":"呢個就唔洗seed啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"739544521cb6936faf3d28dd79c86d563e20cb24","tid":411126,"uid":29317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T14:11:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>到了今年4月時，又有同事發現了沒打馬賽克的版本，兼差拍AV的事情就此曝光</blockquote>"},{"pid":"e7db4a0ef6da1c70b9424e0ad0ad1c7f7ecd4277","tid":411126,"uid":5462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T14:14:03.000Z","msg":"以為睇gv <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eb8224a6db3a3e8ae52b4ff03fd344dd40e3b30","tid":411126,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T14:19:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2813/d2813476.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2813%2Fd2813476.jpg&h=3528f5e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n條女好熟口面，但唔記得名"},{"pid":"058f69e02f06b36371a7934a5948ed93bac945a8","tid":411126,"uid":1789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T14:23:12.000Z","msg":"幾正<br />\n屌女優仲要收翻一千蚊港紙一套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85a4c486f9e7c6755bb1eb6efe58ef8533a974d9","tid":411126,"uid":56833,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T14:23:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>&lt;img src=&quot;<a href=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2813/d2813476.jpg&quot;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2813%2Fd2813476.jpg%22&d=CU0xZXF8PN25iZTvszaXNJUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=b4de84e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2813/d2813476.jpg&quot;</a>  /&gt;<br />\n<br />\n條女好熟口面，但唔記得名</blockquote><br />\n三上悠亞都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6958cf3d2aef7bf15c682f25ac805a40a9096a91","tid":411126,"uid":23887,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T14:24:42.000Z","msg":"基沙文對於這宗交易非常歡迎，希望哥斯達回歸有助球隊增加戰